WITH TopSuppliers AS (
    SELECT s.s_suppkey, s.s_name, SUM(ps.ps_supplycost * ps.ps_availqty) AS total_supply_cost
    FROM supplier s
    JOIN partsupp ps ON s.s_suppkey = ps.ps_suppkey
    GROUP BY s.s_suppkey, s.s_name
    ORDER BY total_supply_cost DESC
    LIMIT 10
),
CustomerOrders AS (
    SELECT c.c_custkey, c.c_name, SUM(o.o_totalprice) AS total_orders
    FROM customer c
    JOIN orders o ON c.c_custkey = o.o_custkey
    GROUP BY c.c_custkey, c.c_name
),
NationRegion AS (
    SELECT n.n_nationkey, n.n_name, r.r_name
    FROM nation n
    JOIN region r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey
)
SELECT 
    tr.s_name AS supplier_name,
    co.c_name AS customer_name,
    nr.n_name AS nation_name,
    COALESCE(SUM(lo.l_extendedprice * (1 - lo.l_discount)), 0) AS total_revenue,
    COUNT(DISTINCT o.o_orderkey) AS total_orders_count
FROM TopSuppliers tr
JOIN partsupp ps ON tr.s_suppkey = ps.ps_suppkey
JOIN lineitem lo ON ps.ps_partkey = lo.l_partkey
JOIN orders o ON lo.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey
JOIN customer co ON o.o_custkey = co.c_custkey
JOIN NationRegion nr ON co.c_nationkey = nr.n_nationkey
WHERE lo.l_shipdate BETWEEN '1997-01-01' AND '1997-12-31' AND o.o_orderstatus = 'F'
GROUP BY tr.s_name, co.c_name, nr.n_name
ORDER BY total_revenue DESC

SELECT COALESCE("t8"."SUPPLIER_NAME", "t8"."SUPPLIER_NAME") AS "SUPPLIER_NAME", "t8"."CUSTOMER_NAME", "t8"."NATION_NAME", CAST("t8"."FD_D_f6" AS DECIMAL(19, 4)) AS "TOTAL_REVENUE", "t8"."TOTAL_ORDERS_COUNT"
FROM (SELECT "t2"."S_NAME", "customer"."c_name", "t4"."N_NAME", MIN("t2"."S_NAME") AS "SUPPLIER_NAME", MIN("customer"."c_name") AS "CUSTOMER_NAME", MIN("t4"."N_NAME") AS "NATION_NAME", SUM("t5"."l_extendedprice" * (1 - "t5"."l_discount")) AS "FD_D_f6", COUNT(DISTINCT "t3"."o_orderkey") AS "TOTAL_ORDERS_COUNT"
FROM (SELECT "supplier"."s_suppkey" AS "S_SUPPKEY", "supplier"."s_name" AS "S_NAME", SUM("partsupp"."ps_supplycost" * "partsupp"."ps_availqty") AS "TOTAL_SUPPLY_COST"
FROM "supplier"
INNER JOIN "partsupp" ON "supplier"."s_suppkey" = "partsupp"."ps_suppkey"
GROUP BY "supplier"."s_suppkey", "supplier"."s_name"
ORDER BY 3 DESC NULLS FIRST
LIMIT 10) AS "t2"
INNER JOIN ((SELECT *
FROM "orders"
WHERE "o_orderstatus" = 'F') AS "t3" INNER JOIN ((SELECT "nation"."n_nationkey" AS "N_NATIONKEY", "nation"."n_name" AS "N_NAME", "region"."r_name" AS "R_NAME"
FROM "region"
INNER JOIN "nation" ON "region"."r_regionkey" = "nation"."n_regionkey") AS "t4" INNER JOIN "customer" ON "t4"."N_NATIONKEY" = "customer"."c_nationkey") ON "t3"."o_custkey" = "customer"."c_custkey" INNER JOIN ("partsupp" AS "partsupp0" INNER JOIN (SELECT *
FROM "s1"
WHERE "l_shipdate" >= DATE '1997-01-01' AND "l_shipdate" <= DATE '1997-12-31') AS "t5" ON "partsupp0"."ps_partkey" = "t5"."l_partkey") ON "t3"."o_orderkey" = "t5"."l_orderkey") ON "t2"."S_SUPPKEY" = "partsupp0"."ps_suppkey"
GROUP BY "t2"."S_NAME", "customer"."c_name", "t4"."N_NAME"
ORDER BY 7 DESC NULLS FIRST) AS "t8"
